org.apache.calcite.sql.validate

Class TableScope

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.sql.validate.DelegatingScope
      • org.apache.calcite.sql.validate.ListScope
        • org.apache.calcite.sql.validate.TableScope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SqlValidatorScope

    class TableScope
extends ListScope
    The name-resolution scope of a LATERAL TABLE clause.

    The objects visible are those in the parameters found on the left side of the LATERAL TABLE clause, and objects inherited from the parent scope.
